dct_description_sm: This point data layer represents private use heliports in Wisconsin in 2018. The dataset was originally published by the Wisconsin Department of Transportation. This shapefile was originally part of a larger dataset of airport reference points.[Wisconsin Private Use Heliports - Airport Reference Points][Wisconsin Private Use Heliports - Airport Reference Points]
